Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:02.400
There continue to be new APIs added to the web

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:05.850
platform, as well. For example, there's an upcoming API that

00:00:05.850 --> 00:00:10.340
adds haptic feedback to the web, the vibration API. This

00:00:10.340 --> 00:00:13.510
API is currently available in Firefox and coming soon in

00:00:13.510 --> 00:00:16.660
Chrome for Android. This enables you to use the mobile

00:00:16.660 --> 00:00:20.560
device's shaker device. To buzz in the users hand, just

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:22.430
like when you have your phone set to vibrate and

00:00:22.430 --> 00:00:25.350
you get a call, this can be really useful for letting

00:00:25.350 --> 00:00:29.560
the user know something is happening ,particularly for errors or notifications.

